<section class="cfs-section">
    <h2 id="what-can-you-talk-about"><a href="#what-can-you-talk-about">What Can You Talk About?</a></h2>
    <p>We welcome sessions of any length—from <strong>lightning talks (5 minutes)</strong> to <strong>in-depth deep dives (up to 90 minutes)</strong>. Topics can be:</p>
    <div class="cfs-topics-grid">
        <div class="cfs-topic-card">
            <h3>Technical Topics</h3>
            <p>Building scalable applications, DevOps, cloud platforms, testing strategies, architecture patterns, and more.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="cfs-topic-card">
            <h3>Soft Skills</h3>
            <p>Code reviews, communication, mentoring, team dynamics, and collaboration techniques.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="cfs-topic-card">
            <h3>Career & Wellbeing</h3>
            <p>Career progression, mental health in tech, work-life balance, and professional growth.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="cfs-topic-card">
            <h3>Emerging Tech</h3>
            <p>AI, new languages, frameworks, tools, and trends shaping the industry.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <p class="cfs-topic-inspiration">Need inspiration? Previous talks have covered: Building Scalable Web Apps • Effective Code Reviews • DevOps Pipelines • Cybersecurity • Cloud Platforms • Accessibility • AI for Developers • Git Mastery • Testing Strategies • Ethics in Software • Microservices • Performance Optimization • UX for Developers • And more!</p>
</section>

