<section class="cfs-section">
    <h2 id="support-offered"><a href="#support-offered">Support & Resources</a></h2>
    <p>We've curated resources to help you prepare an amazing talk:</p>
    <div class="cfs-resources-grid">
        <div class="cfs-resource">
            <h3>Planning & Ideas</h3>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="https://speaking.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">speaking.io</a> — How to become a speaker</li>
