            <h3>Slides & Demos</h3>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="https://slides.google.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Slides</a> — Free, easy, collaborative</li>
                <li><a href="https://dev.to/estruyf/making-live-coding-demos-easier-with-demo-time-d8o#" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Demo Time</a> — Live code demo tool</li>
