                <li>📞 Schedule a practice run with us</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
    <aside class="cfs-tips">
        <h3>Pro Tips</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Font size:</strong> 20pt minimum so the back row can read your slides</li>
            <li><strong>Background:</strong> Avoid pure black—it doesn't show up well on camera</li>
            <li><strong>No internet?</strong> Have a backup plan for live demos (pre-recorded clips, local files, etc.)</li>
            <li><strong>Speaker notes:</strong> Use them—they're your safety net</li>
        </ul>
    </aside>
</section>

